'''Fionnula Flanagan''' (born [[December 10]], [[1940s|1941]])<ref name="This Week Fett" /> portrayed [[Catarine Towani]] in ''[[Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure]]''.<ref name="Caravan of Courage" />

Flanagan was one of the few actors (along with [[Phil Fondacaro]], [[Felix Silla]], [[Clive Revill]] and [[Jason Wingreen]]) to be involved in both a ''[[Star Wars]]'' film and a [[Wikipedia:Star Trek|Star Trek]] production. Flanagan played [[Memoryalpha:Juliana Tainer|Juliana Tainer]] in the [[Wikipedia:Star Trek: The Next Generation|''Star Trek: The Next Generation'']] episode "Inheritance", [[Memoryalpha:Enina Tandro|Enina Tandro]] in the [[Wikipedia:Star Trek: Deep Space Nine|''Star Trek: Deep Space Nine'']] episode "Dax", and [[Memoryalpha:V'Lar|Ambassador V'Lar]] in the [[Wikipedia:Star Trek: Enterprise|''Star Trek: Enterprise'']] episode "Fallen Hero". Recently, she portrayed [http://lostpedia.wikia.com/wiki/Eloise_Hawking Eloise Hawking] in [[Wikipedia:American Broadcasting Company|ABC's]] TV show [[Wikipedia:Lost (TV series)|Lost]].

